title: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
headline: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
subtitle: Lime Leopard Slab Cap and Lime Leopard Slab Canvas Shoes
content:
Your gift of the Lime Leopard Slab cap and Lime Leopard Slab Canvas shoes for completing all 5 Last Dose missions will be added to your wardrobe before April 7.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon.
